OL,3,CHome Secretary to hold meeting on
OL,4,C'alarming rise' in intimidation
OL,6,FThe Home Secretary Yvette Cooper will
OL,7,Fhold a meeting to address the
OL,8,F"alarming rise" in harassment,
OL,9,Fintimidation and abuse towards
OL,10,Felection candidates and campaigners.
OL,12,FIt comes after the government's
OL,13,Fadvisor on political violence wrote a
OL,14,Fletter to Cooper warning of the growth
OL,15,Fof a "toxic, dangerous environment" in
OL,16,Fpublic life, and urging her to
OL,17,Fcommission an inquiry into
OL,18,Fintimidation of candidates.
