OL,3,CHome Secretary to hold meeting on
OL,4,C'alarming rise' in intimidation
OL,6,FCooper condemned some of the
OL,7,F"disgraceful scenes" during the
OL,8,Felection campaign, as many candidates
OL,9,Ffaced threats, particularly over the
OL,10,Fissue of Gaza.
OL,12,FThe meeting of the government
OL,13,Ftaskforce on defending democracy will
OL,14,Flook at how "public safety, security
OL,15,Fand standards in our democracy can be
OL,16,Fupheld."
