OL,3,CHome Secretary to hold meeting on
OL,4,C'alarming rise' in intimidation
OL,6,FJohn Woodcock, the government's
OL,7,Fadvisor on political violence, wrote
OL,8,Fto Cooper on Friday expressing concern
OL,9,Fthat intimidation of election
OL,10,Fcandidates could have been a
OL,11,F"concerted campaign by extremists".
OL,13,FIn an interview with the Guardian
OL,14,Fnewspaper, Woodcock drew parallels
OL,15,Fwith the assassination attempt on
OL,16,FDonald Trump, saying it was a "vivid
OL,17,Freminder of the vulnerability of all
OL,18,Fpoliticians."
