OL,3,CHome Secretary to hold meeting on
OL,4,C'alarming rise' in intimidation
OL,6,FWoodcock urged Cooper to launch an
OL,7,Finquiry to look at whether the
OL,8,Fprotestors in different constituencies
OL,9,Fwere working together.
OL,11,FIt was female candidates in particular
OL,12,Fwho were targeted during the election
OL,13,Fcampaign - Justice Secretary Shabana
OL,14,FMahmood said masked men interrupted a
OL,15,Fcommunity meeting, while Jess Phillips
OL,16,Fsaid her staff had to make regular
OL,17,Fcalls to police about safety threats.
OL,19,FPhillips was also heckled during her
OL,20,Fspeech after she was re-elected as the
OL,21,FMP for Birmingham Yardley.
