OL,3,CHome Secretary to hold meeting on
OL,4,C'alarming rise' in intimidation
OL,6,FThe Home Secretary said: "Political
OL,7,Fviolence, intimidation and harassment
OL,8,Fhave no place in our democracy.
OL,10,F"The recent General Election campaign
OL,11,Fdemonstrated some of the great
OL,12,Fstrengths of our democratic
OL,13,Ftraditions, including a smooth and
OL,14,Fpeaceful transition of power from one
OL,15,Fparty to another, but during this
OL,16,Fcampaign we also saw an alarming rise
OL,17,Fin intimidation, harassment and abuse
OL,18,Ftowards candidates, campaigners and
OL,19,Fvolunteers from all parties which
OL,20,Fsimply cannot be tolerated.
