OL,3,CHome Secretary to hold meeting on
OL,4,C'alarming rise' in intimidation
OL,6,F"Some of those incidents are now being
OL,7,Finvestigated by the police. The
OL,8,Fdisgraceful scenes we saw in some
OL,9,Fareas during this election campaign
OL,10,Fmust not be repeated", she said.
OL,12,F"That's why I am convening and
OL,13,Fchairing a meeting of the Defending
OL,14,FDemocracy Taskforce next week to make
OL,15,Fsure public safety, security and
OL,16,Fstandards in our democracy can be
OL,17,Fupheld."
