OL,3,CHome Secretary to hold meeting on
OL,4,C'alarming rise' in intimidation
OL,6,FCooper said she will also be speaking
OL,7,Fwith MPs and candidates who faced
OL,8,F"intimidation, harassment and abuse
OL,9,Fduring the election campaign", to hear
OL,10,Fabout their experiences.
OL,12,FThe Defending Democracy taskforce was
OL,13,Fset up in November last year to
OL,14,F"protect the democratic integrity of
OL,15,Fthe UK from foreign interference."
OL,17,FConcerns around the security of MPs
OL,18,Fhave been heightened since the murders
OL,19,Fof Labour MP Jo Cox in 2016, and
OL,20,FConservative MP David Amess in 2016 at
OL,21,Fa constituency surgery.
